OL,6,FComedy couple Jon Richardson and Lucy
OL,7,FBeaumont are divorcing after nine
OL,8,Fyears of marriage, they have announced
OL,9,Fin a joint statement.
OL,11,FThe couple have starred in Meet The
OL,12,FRichardsons, in which they play
OL,13,F"exaggerated versions of themselves",
OL,14,Fsince 2020.
OL,16,FThe "at home mockumentary" series
OL,17,Freturned to Dave's UKTV on April 8 for
OL,18,Fits fifth series.
