OL,3,CComedy couple Jon Richardson and Lucy
OL,4,CBeaumont announce divorce
OL,6,F"After nine years of marriage, we
OL,7,Fwould like to announce that we have
OL,8,Fseparated," the pair said in a
OL,9,Fstatement posted on social media.
OL,11,F"We have jointly and amicably made the
OL,12,Fdifficult decision to divorce and go
OL,13,Four separate ways.
OL,15,F"As our only priority is managing this
OL,16,Fdifficult transition for our daughter,
OL,17,Fwe would ask that our privacy is
OL,18,Frespected at this sensitive time to
OL,19,Fprotect her well-being.
OL,21,F"We will be making no further comment."
